snippet: Anthony D. Weiner, a candidate for New York City mayor, said in an interview that he had come up with the term, but an aide later said that Mr. Weiner meant he was the first on the left to embrace it unapologetically.
abstract: New York City mayoral candidate Anthony D Weiner says in interview that he had come up with the term Obamacare, but an aide later says that Weiner meant he was the first person on the left to embrace it unapologetically.
